I'm a postdoctoral researcher at [Insper](https://www.insper.edu.br/en/) in São Paulo, Brazil.

My main research project at the moment examines the potential effects of a policy intended to reduce domestic violence on the labor market. This research in [financed](http://bv.fapesp.br/pt/bolsas/207019/) by the São Paulo Research Foundation (FAPESP).

I a have a broad interest in topics of development economics with a focus on education, labor and political economy.

My email address is [`vinicius.gomes.lima [at] alumni.usp.br`](mailto:vinicius.gomes.lima@alumni.usp.br).
